name: Top Monthly Chat
description: For members actively engaging in text chats. Open to everyone!

name: Top Monthly Voice
description: Given to members who frequently join and contribute in voice channels.

name: Official Chatbot
description: specifically for Official Chat Bots. This role is assigned to bots that assist with server interactions.

name: Community Manager
description: specifically for admins. Also considered the highest position among server staff.

name: Division Manager
description: specifically for Division Managers. Also considered the second-highest position among server staff.

name: Head Division
description: specifically for Head Division. Also considered the third-highest position among server staff.

name: Team Management
description: specifically for Team Management. This role includes all staff members from any division.

name: Trainee
description: specifically for Trainees. This role is for new staff members who are still in training.

name: Contributor
description: given to those who have donated at least 50k to the server. All members can have it.

name: Donator
description: given to those who have donated at least 10k to the server. All members can have it.

name: Booster
description: given to those who boost the server with Nitro.

name: Benefactor
description: given to those who donate to the server in the form of owo currency/owocash.

name: Supporter
description: given to those who place the server link in their Discord bio.

name: Special
description: given to those considered special by the server admins, usually their friends.
